channel.title: Teletab Help
channel.description: I know this is my like 3rd post of trying to get help today. Lol. I am trying to make teletabs teleport me. I researched all about the item id of the teletab, (8013) and I found out that it is 'disabled temporarily', obviously this was set by the before-coder. Now how would I make this start a teleport?

item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket

You need to implement it under the UseItem Packet, I believe it’s 53. From there It’s just like a regular teleport.
